Consider the following Python code snippet. It processes user input to generate a specific output. The code involves nested loops, conditional statements, and string manipulation.  What will be the output if the user inputs the string 'Hello World!'? 

```python
input_string = input("Enter a string: ")
output_string = ''
for i in range(len(input_string)):
    if input_string[i].isalpha():
        if i % 2 == 0:
            output_string += input_string[i].upper()
        else:
            output_string += input_string[i].lower()
    else:
        output_string += input_string[i]
print(output_string)
```
